<h1 id="communication">Communication</h1>

<p>We communicate through many channels. Use the
<a href="/manual/guides/communication">communication</a> guide to understand and be
prepared to make use of the various meetings, listhosts, chat media, calendars,
twitter accounts, and whatnot that tie us together.</p>

